<h2 id="internationalization%20(i18n)">Internationalization (i18n)</h2>
<p>Select2 supports multiple languages by simply including the right language JS<br>file (<code>dist/js/i18n/it.js</code>, <code>dist/js/i18n/nl.js</code>, etc.) after<br><code>dist/js/select2.js</code>.</p>
<p>Missing a language? Just copy <code>src/js/select2/i18n/en.js</code>, translate it, and<br>make a pull request back to Select2 here on GitHub.</p>
